patch.comment: Fix an issue where builds running on Windows and not on the C drive would not discover assets.
Fix line endings in published package.
Fix an issue where globbing assets from a NPM package would fail on Windows.

major.comment: Add support for Webpack 5 and drop support for Webpack 4.

patch.comment: Update type-only imports to include the type modifier.

minor.comment: Apply webpack's "output.hashSalt" configuration property (if present) to the folder hash.

patch.comment: Fix an issue where the plugin will throw if the folder being required contains subfolders.
Fix a link in the README.
